1.25rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170210/1486713392883743.jpg\" title=\"优秀节目得主.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; float: none;\"/></p><p><br/></p>','a:1:{i:0;a:2:{s:4:\"path\";s:68:\"/xfzz/web/Attached/pic/20170210/eea88b0bb2fbf6d291114877232efc99.jpg\";s:4:\"name\";s:7:\"eddfaf5\";}}',1,'a:0:{}','a:0:{}',0,0,0,1,1,NULL,1,0,99,1486713365,1486713398,NULL,NULL);
INSERT INTO `voc_art` VALUES (16,14,NULL,'新丰中职召开“有效课堂”第二阶段总结会',NULL,1486656000,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015年12月11日下午4:30，新丰中职“有效课堂”第二阶段总结会在校会议室召开。','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">2015年12月11日下午4:30，新丰中职“有效课堂”第二阶段总结会在校会议室召开。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">以深化职业教育课堂改革为核心，以转变教师的教学方式和学生的学习方式为重点，以高效课堂教学理念为推手，新丰中职2014年3月开展以“有效课堂”为教学法的教学改革，要求在课堂中树立就业教育理念、重点培养学生的动手能力和自学能力。2015学年， “有效课堂”的开展进入“全面展开”的第二阶段，学校课改小组进行了为期三个月的循环听课并进行评奖和召开总结会。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">总结会由潘继武副校长主持，教务处副主任袁必策对循环听课情况做汇报性总结；，教务处主任谭雪霞宣读第一次评课获奖名单并进行了表彰；获得一等奖的杜德金老师分享了自己的教学方法和教学心得；最后，江青平校长做了总结性讲话，要求全体教师务必树立“就业”教学理念，要达到送出去的学生 “上岗即就业”的教学效果，要让学生在企业坐得稳、留得住、升得起！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">学校“有效课堂”的改革还处于初级阶段，相信我校的教师经过一系列教学活动会更加锐意进取，不断改进和提高自己的教育教学水平！</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 32px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">（撰稿人：罗秋雯 &nbsp;审稿人：江青平）</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.25rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170210/1486713483757617.jpg\" title=\"“有效课堂”竞赛一等奖获得者：杜德金老师.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.25rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170210/1486713483555798.jpg\" title=\"“有效课堂表彰大会”现场01.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 1.25rem; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1;\"><img src=\"/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170210/1486713483218816.jpg\" title=\"“有效课堂表彰大会”现场02.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; display: block; float: none;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: