INSERT INTO `voc_art` VALUES (26,15,NULL,'我校教师编排的舞蹈杀入韶关四强，晋级省决赛',NULL,1486656000,'',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2015年9月19日下午2时，新丰县广场舞协会的二十四名队员在县政协副主席冯南燕、县组织部副部长、县老干局局长梁小莉的带领下一行30多人到韶关市中山公园参加由广东电视台举办的《舞动人生》2015年广东省广场舞群英会韶关赛区的比赛，并一举在二十三支参赛队伍中脱颖而出晋级四强，夺取参加省赛的资格。','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">2015<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">年9</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">月19</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">日下午2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">时，新丰县广场舞协会的二十四名队员在县政协副主席冯南燕、县组织部副部长、县老干局局长梁小莉的带领下一行30</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">多人到韶关市中山公园参加由广东电视台举办的《舞动人生》2015</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">年广东省广场舞群英会韶关赛区的比赛，并一举在二十三支参赛队伍中脱颖而出晋级四强，夺取参加省赛的资格。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">新丰县本次参赛的曲目是《微笑人生》，该舞蹈的动作教练是新丰职中的罗秋雯、刘璐两位教师，参赛编排和排练是罗秋雯老师，罗秋雯老师并作为主要演员参赛。本次比赛从接到通知到参赛共历时10<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: inherit; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box;\">天，时间紧、任务重，队员们训练异常刻苦。功夫不负有心人，二十四位姑娘比赛结束后，评委老师点评时连声叫“好”！在点评过程中，评委老师认为舞蹈的编排新颖、有创意，姑娘们的演绎完整表达了舞曲的思想的主题。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.2rem; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: Arial, Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-stretch: inherit; line-height: 33px; vertical-align: baseline; outline: none; box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; widows: 1; text-indent: 28px; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margi